pr_body:
This changes the following:
- Adds a new feature of stopping running or pending pipelines from UI.
- Create a new case for updating (PUT) the pipeline status.
- Adds jx-pipeline as a dependency.
- Adds a modal component.
- Removes `svelte-bootstrap-icons` from package.json

pr_title: feat: btn in table to stop pipelines
pr_body:
- This create another column in pipelines table for ACTIONS.
- Removes start btn from the PipelineDetailPage.

pr_title: fix: add msg field to pipelineActivity Spec and Steps
pr_body:
- Tekton PipelineRun provides the message & this PR will add that Message field to Spec and Steps in the pipelineActivity.
- This PR also adds test for 4 testcases:
	- timeout
	- cancelled
	- success
	- timedout-success
- This also adds the message fields to the expected.yaml.
- Instead of using `testhelpers.AssertTextFilesEqual` we're now just comparing the generated pa and expected pa.
- Also removes `t.TempDir()`
- Adds comments to help understand the steps
- fixes linter.sh

related to https://github.com/jenkins-x/jx-ui/issues/23

Signed-off-by: rajatgupta24 <rajat2411gupta@gmail.com>
